    "abstract": [
        {
            "text": "Please cite this article as: J. Ma, P. Xia, Y. Zhou, et al., Potential effect of blood purification therapy in reducing cytokine storm as a late complication of severe COVID-19, Clinical Immunology (2020), https://doi.",
